<span class="displaytext">(candidate full) made the following statement today regarding the passing of former new york yankee phil rizzuto: <p>"i send my deepest condolences to cora and the rizzuto family for the loss of a truly great yankee. </p><p>"as a lifelong yankee fan, phil was one of my childhood heroes. he was also the yankee announcer i grew up with and it was a great privilege for me later in life to become his friend. </p><p>"he was an excellent ballplayer, superb announcer, one of the greatest bunters in the history of baseball and a truly fine person. everyone will miss the yankee scooter."</p></span>



